  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and let them sizzle for 30 seconds.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and grated ginger, cooking until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add diced carrot and frozen peas, sautéing until the carrot is tender, about 3 minutes.",
    "Push the vegetables to the side and pour in the cold rice, breaking up any clumps.",
    "Season the rice with salt, black pepper, and coriander powder, stirring to combine.",
    "Fold in shredded V Sterbottensost cheese and saffron water, cooking until the cheese melts and the mixture is heated through, about 4 minutes.",
    "Squeeze optional lemon juice over the rice, give a final stir, and serve hot."
